Name:                yaop
Version:             0.1.1.1
Synopsis:            Yet another option parser
Description:
  A simple wrapper over the standard System.Console.GetOpt to make options
  defining more convenient.
License:             BSD3
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Eugene Smolanka <smolanka.zhacka@gmail.com>
Maintainer:          Eugene Smolanka <smolanka.zhacka@gmail.com>
Category:            System
Build-type:          Simple

Extra-source-files:  examples/ex1.hs
                   , examples/ex2.hs

Cabal-version:       >=1.6

Source-repository head
    type: darcs
    location: https://patch-tag.com/repo/zhacka/yaop

Library
  Exposed-modules:     System.Console.YAOP
  Build-depends:       base>=4.2 && <5
                     , template-haskell
                     , mtl>=2.0 && <2.1
